&lt;p&gt;In our native United Kingdom, we released 12 studio albums, 13 extended plays (EPs), including one double EP, and 22 singles. Our &lt;strong&gt;UK discography&lt;/strong&gt; is considered the &lt;strong&gt;&quot;core catalogue&quot;&lt;/strong&gt;, as it contains the albums, EPs and singles released the way the band intended.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is the list of our released 12 studio albums and compilation &lt;strong&gt;&quot;Past Masters&quot;&lt;/strong&gt; which include the recordings released from 1962 to 1970 that are not present on the UK albums.&lt;/p&gt;

